title: Ep 140: You're Gonna Die One Day, So Just Do it ALL!
description: Mommy P gets say deep on it the day her Netflix Special drops. Existence, meaning, purpose, winners and losers - all of it. I answer some emails - should a guy who got his life and got clean from drugs keep his old friends? A boo boo writes in saying he lost 100 pounds but still feels unloveable. What's going on? A lady writes in worried about why she isn't sexually attracted to her hubby. Should she bounce? It's all here, bros. Let's get our lives!
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
